name: Rock Tac Toe
description:
ROCK TAC TOE

Hey everyone, Jason here. Thanks for checking out my first game.

I'll have to come back here and update this description after, you know, I actually playtest the damn thing with another real human being. Those are so hard to come by these days.

In the meantime, let me know what you think. If it's not exciting enough for your modern sensibilities, try wagering some money on it.
